sequenceDiagram
  %% Authored stress fixture (Mermaid@11.12.2): create/destroy inside alt branches with activations.

  participant A as Alice
  participant S as Service

  A->>S: start

  alt spawn worker
    create participant W as Worker
    S->>W: spawn
    activate W
    W-->>S: ready
    deactivate W
    destroy W
    S-xW: terminate
  else reuse
    S->>S: reuse existing worker
    Note right of S: no new participants
  end

  S-->>A: done

